        <outline text="Motivation #CI7130_Intro #CI6240_proto1 #slide #CI7160-intro #basic #CI7110 ">
          <outline text="We are all concerned, but we don't always understand the threats, how possible solutions are designed -- and how we can use them to protect ourselves." />
          <outline text="Who of you has been affected by computer security incidents? " />
          <outline text="Discussion:">
            <outline text="What are typical threats in computer security?" />
            <outline text="What is computer security? What are the different fields in the security domain?" />
