        <outline text="Current Security Challenges #slide #CI7130_Intro  #basic">
          <outline text="Scale of the problem is widely underestimated" />
          <outline text="Nature of the threats often unknown, even to IT professionals" />
          <outline text="Security policies are not sufficiently well-developed" />
          <outline text="There are no standards regulating Internet trading" />
          <outline text="There is no international legislation" />
          <outline text="Common misconceptions about security:">
            <outline text="Myth 1: We need better/stronger encryption algorithms" />
            <outline text="Myth 2: Security is all about encryption" />
            <outline text="Myth 3: Technology is enough to protect our systems" />
            <outline text="Myth 4: Your information on the internet will remain confidential as long as it is encrypted" />
          </outline>
        </outline>
