                </outline>
              </outline>
              <outline text="Software is also data, so all the data vulnerabilities apply" />
              <outline text="Software vulnerabilities are indexed in the CVE catalogue on &lt;a href=&quot;http://cve.org&quot;&gt;cve.org&lt;/a&gt; " />
            </outline>
            <outline text="Data Vulnerabilities #slide #CI7130_Intro ">
              <outline text="Data can be human-readable (text) or binary" />
              <outline text="Enormous amounts  of data around (big data), connected and exposed to the Internet, and stored on corporate clouds" />
              <outline text="Need to think of data at rest, and in transit (computation/memory, harddisk, network, brain). " />
